-- DML: The Build Depot (TBD) — Complete Demo Database Population
-- =============================================================================
-- Single-purpose DML file. Contains NO DDL (CREATE/ALTER/DROP).
-- Fully deterministic — produces identical results on every run.
--
-- Theme: "The Build Depot (TBD)" — a multi-location hardware store chain
-- selling products from brands that sound *almost* real.
--
-- Prerequisites:
--   Run ddl.sql first to create the schema and all tables.
--
-- Scenarios supported:
--   A — Inventory Misallocation (shipments vs actual stock)
--   B — Faulty Products (defective return rates by vendor)
--   C — Customer Segmentation (VIP, Big Spender, Category-Loyal)
-- =============================================================================

